OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHow India's first deaf     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flawyer made history in top 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcourt                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Last week, Sarah Sunny made history    
OL,6, after she became India's first deaf    
OL,7, lawyer to argue in the country's       
OL,8, Supreme Court.                         
OL,10,FThe 27-year-old first appeared before  
OL,11,FChief Justice DY Chandrachud in        
OL,12,FSeptember after the court made an      
OL,13,Fexception and allowed a sign language  
OL,14,Finterpreter to assist her with the     
OL,15,Farguments.                             
OL,17,FOn 6 October, the court also appointed 
OL,18,Fits own interpreter for Ms Sunny, the  
OL,19,Ffirst in the court's history, so that  
OL,20,F"she could understand what was going   
OL,21,Fon" during the proceedings.            
